{"id":150642,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/毛泽东1958年为何说“我们超过秦始皇一百倍”/","date":"2011-05-08T04:27:50Z","modified":"2011-05-08T04:27:50Z","title":"毛泽东1958年为何说“我们超过秦始皇一百倍”","content":"<p>毛泽东当着一二千与会代表的面发表了这样一番高论：秦始皇算什么？他只坑了四百六十个儒，我们坑了四万六千个儒，我们镇反，还没有杀掉一些反革命的知识分子吗？我与民主人士辩论过&#8230;<img src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/t1/502438129/hihistory/feedsky/s.gif?r=http://hihistory.net/post/11105/\" border=\"0\" height=\"0\" width=\"0\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/l/feedsky/hihistory/502438129/art01.html\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/i/feedsky/hihistory/502438129/art01.gif\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/6G-ZGhLNjN8VY_ROkMI_LQrAL7Q/0/da\"><img src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/6G-ZGhLNjN8VY_ROkMI_LQrAL7Q/0/di\" border=\"0\" ismap=\"ismap\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/6G-ZGhLNjN8VY_ROkMI_LQrAL7Q/1/da\"><img src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/6G-ZGhLNjN8VY_ROkMI_LQrAL7Q/1/di\" border=\"0\" ismap=\"ismap\" /></a></p>\n</p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[20534],"tags":[9091]}